Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,听说是日本人？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是亚洲的国家吧 会切腹什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面 堀川阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到阿尔比昂王国
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,蒙公主亲自迎接 不胜荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是觉得应付远东岛国这种活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我们的花瓶公主就够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这是把风险也考虑进来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.99,0:00:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有人图谋暗杀的传闻应该也传到皇室耳朵里了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,组织暗杀的主谋是藤堂十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,听说他以一人之力斩杀了百人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不开化的小国的传闻倒是够夸张 不知道能信多少
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是欧洲派遣过去的军事顾问发来的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,据说戊辰战争中他曾经孤身闯上装甲舰将其击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:12.57,Reference,,0,0,0,,**戊辰战争，发生于日本庆应·明治年间的新政府与江户幕府的战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊 难得拉拢到的公主万一被卷进暗杀骚动可就不好办了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.34,0:01:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Principal就是用来对付这种局面的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,**车头前的徽章是英国皇室徽章。盾面上两组三只金狮象征英格兰，红狮象征苏格兰，竖琴象征北爱尔兰。周围写有古法语Honi soit qui mal y pense（心怀邪念者蒙羞），下方饰带上写有法语Dieu et mon droit（我权天授）。盾两侧是代表英格兰的狮子和苏格兰的独角兽。盾上方为头盔、圣爱德华王冠和狮子。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我让人准备了皇室专用列车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,请您乘这趟车前往伦敦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,为我等如此大费周章 感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,此次旅途还请多加关照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,日本人真怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得日本人应该也不想被黑蜥蜴星人这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:03:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:39.49,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,#05 案件7 枪与剑之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,堀川阁下是为了修订条约而来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,**日本曾于江户幕府的安政五年与美国、俄国、荷兰、英国、法国缔结通商条约（安政五国条约），承认对方的治外法权，放弃日本的关税自主权，无条件给予对方单方向最惠国待遇。明治维新后，日本进行了一系列外交上的努力，力图修正条约挽回不利局面。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的条约实在太过不平等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 这也是此前我等的无知招致
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,堀川大人 在这里恐怕不便谈及此事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们感受到了堀川阁下的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我没有任何决定权
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但我承诺会让您与祖母大人会面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不胜感激 实在不胜感激
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,列车可是在行驶着啊 应该不会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,西洋女人真是无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,问别人名字时应该先报上姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是藤堂十兵卫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到是个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,两支手枪 戴在怀里和腰后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还有左边的鞋子 做了什么手脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,有轻微的金属声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人闯进来 不愧是传说中的杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,多萝西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,世界真是广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到西洋居然会有体术如此高超的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是 看来斩杀百人的名号不假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人不是刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,请停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不是敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,千世阁下 你为什么来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,明知故问 我是来斩杀藤堂十兵卫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为此我才远赴这异国之地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也不能让你一个人回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就先允许你同行至伦敦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我定会保护好您的安全 铲除逆贼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,只是带你去而已 你不必上阵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我比其他任何武士都了解藤堂十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我反对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不能让来路不明的人乘上公主所在的列车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你在怀疑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,至少你确实是偷渡来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就来证明自己值不值得信任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩都消停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,千世阁下 请放下刀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,安洁 你和千世搭档<buddy>吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,搭档<buddy>…搭档<buddy>？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就是伙伴的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我和这个女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,公主 这笑话可不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这位小姐是危险人物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就更得交给值得信赖的人监视了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,五号车厢和末端车厢上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有五十名铁道警卫小队的队员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一般的袭击是伤不到堀川阁下的性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,十兵卫的袭击可不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你和十兵卫交过手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么和他交手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为了自己的理念？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还是因为跟随的主人不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这是在审问我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,身为搭档 当然要互相了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我出身于佐贺藩 士族 16岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,**佐贺藩，又称肥前藩，日本中受西方科技影响较早，是推进明治维新的「萨长土肥」四藩之一。藩内受宣扬武士道的《叶隐》影响深刻。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,**明治维新后，旧武士阶级及地下家、公家和寺院的佣人中受禄非华族的人被归为士族一级。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢酱菜 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,安洁 17岁 生在黑蜥蜴星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 难怪会掌握那种体术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,辉夜姬也是从月亮来的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,日本有来自月亮的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不止是外星来客 就连神明都在我们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,神明在身边？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,山峦河川 甚至茅房中都有神在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,到伦敦途中只在这个站停靠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果要下手 就肯定会选择这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,别哭了 我来给你赶走痛痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛 痛痛 飞走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛 痛痛 飞走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:09:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是传自父亲的东洋咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他以前也经常对我用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:30.44,Reference,,0,0,0,,**张贴在火车站中的应为1910年前后South Eastern and Chatham Railway(SE&CR)的线路图。SE&CR由South Eastern Railway(SE)和London, Chatham and Dover Railway (LC&DR)这2家公司组成。片中列车从Dover出发至Ashford为SE的线路，Ashford经Maidstone至终点站London的Holborn Viaduct火车站为LC&DR线路。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要帮藤堂十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我对东洋的小岛国没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能把那个女人卷进暗杀事件就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然只是个花瓶 但她的王位继承权排在第四
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,说不准什么时候就会有人推她上位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,结果在梅德斯通站没有发生袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看来十兵卫这般出众的武士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,到了异国他乡也手生了几分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,十兵卫绝非好对付的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你对十兵卫这么了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,十兵卫杀害了我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说 时间一直停在两年前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不能手刃十兵卫 我的眼泪都流不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一直盯着清洁工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是藤堂十兵卫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,请您在此稍等 我去看下情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,为了警备考虑 下行列车应该停运了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此 那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,藤堂十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看来诺曼底公爵履行了他的诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,射出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,让机车后退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要和后方的士兵会合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,两辆车连着 现在减速的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会被拉脱轨的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人要冲进车里了 全员拔刀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下 快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,多萝西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,公主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在五号车厢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,快去 安洁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,用C球还能赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,带我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,十兵卫就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,人手越多越好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,跟上我的节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,零
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你背叛了我们吗 千世阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,背叛者是你们才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,臭丫头…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,把速度提上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,别慢下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,会被拽脱轨的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,铁轨要在前面交会了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,按这个速度撞上 整车人都会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,安洁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别让她们上来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她们到车顶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这体术太强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这里交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,十兵卫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大岛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,堀川阁下 我来取你性命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你个幕府的残党…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,保护阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下 请退后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,小贝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,里面戴着什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:17:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,安洁 停下列车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,关闭调节阀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,推起红手柄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,回动机向右转
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来 打开旁通阀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你变强了 千世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,千世 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,请安心 堀川阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,逆贼藤堂十兵卫已被在下斩杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,十兵卫是你父亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,教过我剑术的温柔父亲早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,葬在这里的是 不过是个叛投敌人的刺客而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:20:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这样…你就能接受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,无需同情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,倒不如说 我很骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我超越了父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 多萝西在等我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,千世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你保护了公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛 痛痛 飞走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛 痛痛 飞走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲的咒语不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,心里的痛 赶不走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这就喝上酒了 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口全愈合了 要看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,转学生 东堂千世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,转学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来了啊 千世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这个房间就是我们的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,上面的人做了交易 让我协助「掉包」计划
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让堀川阁下从王国转投共和国
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就把他引荐给了Control
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候勾…勾引了堀川阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.64,0:22:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,贵族也会用这么粗俗的词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么词能形容你做的勾当…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,安洁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了你 我才能和十兵卫一战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我再次表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.41,0:22:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你要在这个国家生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我就教给你西洋式的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,握手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,西洋式的…也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:24:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me, I say cross the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you feel that nothing turns around
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a gear in sync inside a clock
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who can be sure of how to make it work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Inner sight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta stay alive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never be deceived
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m a girl that sees through lies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz I know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Know it all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna fly so high
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Get across the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What awaits, and what can it show me now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Smack it down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get across the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Break away, and then let’em catch me say
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,“Don’t let me down”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When the clockwork moves and starts to shine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(you got to find)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever let it blow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Show the way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast it off right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.89,0:22:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If days were not the same
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know what I’d do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine me laughing and now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See me walk in the street
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:22:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then catch a red double bus
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And heaven would find me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.78,0:23:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d go on a float
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.56,0:23:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eased up, I smile a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you know
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a scene that I…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.96,0:23:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat in my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.02,0:23:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,While slippin’ a black tea, and now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gently touching a tree
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.41,0:23:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Calming hi-beam from the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can free me, I feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m getting so close
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to laughing sweet with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,(Goin’ out on)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunday morning, the light has come
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,(La la, morning the light’s on me…)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And looking up high
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,(Looking around, you’ll see all around)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanish worries the light has come
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.08,0:23:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,(La la, shining the light on me…)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.54,0:23:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to try for a pleasant “now”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,(Taking me high up, I’m free)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.69,0:24:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a page of life in my story
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.51,0:24:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet and bright
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
